org.hps.readout.util

Class IntegerRingBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.readout.util.RingBuffer<Integer,Integer>
      • org.hps.readout.util.IntegerRingBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Integer>

    public class IntegerRingBuffer
extends RingBuffer<Integer,Integer>
    Class IntegerRingBuffer is an implementation of RingBuffer for integers. Each buffer cell represents a integer value, which can be modified through the method addToCell(int, Object).
